Dataset name: Wooded in parks and green areas of Madrid
Dataset brief description: Description of the trees, state and tree masses present in the historic, singular and forested districts and parks of municipal maintenance of the City of Madrid. NOTE: Due to the change of the municipal computer platform used for the elaboration of the files, and the City Council does not have the updated data for 2018, so the files related to the Treeing, State of the Treeland and Tree Masses in green areas and districts and streets related to that year are not published. You can find more related information on this portal in the dataset Area of parks and green areas of Madrid as well as other information about this data in the Transparency Portal & Wooded in green areas, parks and gardens of Madrid.
